@startuml creative-flow
!theme plain

title Creative Flow (Original & Inspired By)

actor "User / CLI" as User
participant "Orchestrator" as Orch
participant "Claude API" as Claude
participant "TTS Provider" as TTS
participant "Image Provider" as Image
participant "Whisper" as Whisper
participant "FFmpeg" as FFmpeg

note over User
  **Original:** user provides a topic or premise
  **Inspired by:** user provides a source story
end note

User -> Orch: create(mode, input)

== Analysis ==
Orch -> Claude: Analyze source material
Claude --> Orch: craft_notes, thematic_brief,\nsource_stats, characters
Orch -> Orch: Write analysis.json

== Story Bible ==
Orch -> Claude: Create characters, setting, rules
Claude --> Orch: story_bible
Orch -> Orch: Write story_bible.json

== Outline ==
Orch -> Claude: Plan scene beats + word targets
Claude --> Orch: outline (scene list)
Orch -> Orch: Write outline.json

== Scene Prose ==
loop for each scene
  Orch -> Claude: Write scene prose\n(craft_notes + bible + outline + running summary)
  Claude --> Orch: scene prose
  Orch -> Orch: Write scene_NNN.md
end

== Critique & Revision ==
loop for each scene
  Orch -> Claude: Critique scene quality
  Claude --> Orch: revision (if needed)
end

== Image Prompts ==
Orch -> Claude: Generate image prompts\n(character reference + all scene prose)
Claude --> Orch: image prompt per scene

== Narration Prep ==
loop for each scene
  Orch -> Claude: Prepare text for spoken delivery
  Claude --> Orch: modified text + changelog
end

== TTS Generation ==
loop for each scene
  Orch -> TTS: Synthesize narration audio
  TTS --> Orch: audio bytes
  Orch -> Orch: Write scene_NNN.mp3
end

== Image Generation ==
loop for each scene
  Orch -> Image: Generate illustration\n(style_prefix + image_prompt)
  Image --> Orch: PNG image
  Orch -> Orch: Write scene_NNN.png
end

== Caption Generation ==
loop for each scene
  Orch -> Whisper: Transcribe audio
  Whisper --> Orch: word-level timestamps
  Orch -> Orch: Reconcile punctuation from prose
  Orch -> Orch: Write scene_NNN.json + .ass
end

== Video Assembly ==
loop for each scene
  Orch -> FFmpeg: Composite image + audio + captions
  FFmpeg --> Orch: scene_NNN.mp4
end
Orch -> FFmpeg: Concatenate with crossfades
FFmpeg --> Orch: final.mp4

Orch --> User: Done — final.mp4

@enduml
